item.dc:creator: @RANCID RANCID
item.description:
@RANCID wrote:

Habbo hotel is a lame ass online ‘world’ for those who don’t know. Its client is a shockwave app, the protocal was just an open plain text system, but recently the added some encryption to out going packets after I did some things they didn’t enjoy.

Anyway, I am not aware of any existing public cheats/hacks (other than some lame server emulators). Maybe one day I’ll get bored enough to open it up again and write some stuff for it again - but I wouldn’t hold your breath.
